lyn\n|\nLet's do everything that we can, and let the good Lord do everything else that we can't.\n\n- Dr. Jacinta Mpalyenkana, Ph.D, MBA\n|\nLife is a panic, without a prayer.\n\n- Lailah\n|\nThe elements of life do not segregate themselves, unless they are human.\n\n- Zephyr\n|\nWhen you have experienced the depth of your inner self, the idea of enlightenment is no longer a goal to strive towards, but rather an attitude to maintain.\n\n- Gary\n|\nThe world needs great inspires, who will encourage every living soul to reach their highest potential. You can be one.\n\n- Lailah Gifty Akita, Think Great: Be Great!\n|\nOne sign of a great actor is when he can be alone by himself on the screen, doing almost nothing, and producing one of a film's defining moments.\n\n- Roger\n|\nThe less you feed the ego, the stronger you will be.\n\n- Aleksandra Ninkovic, Write like no one is reading\n|\nYou need to find somebody who will speak the same language. We understand that we couldn't have any kind of discussion without permission, without a legal framework behind it.\n\n- Anatoly\n|\nlove being such, or such,the normal corners of your heartwill never guess how muchmy wonderful jealousy is dark\n\n- E.E. Cummings, Complete Poems, 1904-1962\n|\nTo fail at trying is worse than to fail after trying. If we never try, then we never learn.\n\n- Lindsey Rietzsch, Successful Failures: Recognizing the Divine Role That Opposition Plays in Life's Quest for Success\n|\nThe world needs great inspirers, to ignite the light in every soul.\n\n- Lailah Gifty Akita, Think Great: Be Great!\n|\nJust like changing personality, culture change is possible but difficult.\n\n- Pearl Zhu, Change Insight: Change as an Ongoing Capability to Fuel Digital Transformation\n|\nWhen life places stones in your path, be the water. A persistent drop of water will wear away even the hardest stone.\n\n- Autumn\n|\nLove is the only power that heals, connects and includes all.....not by force, but by grace.\n\n- Vivian